Trivia[]

Camille, the Steel Shadow
  • Camille mocks multiple champions and/or their own quotes, in her kill lines:
    • ▶️  "Ashes, ashes, you fall down." references ▶️  "Ashes, ashes, they all fall down."
    • ▶️  "Next time, take the map." references ▶️  "Who needs a map?!"
    • ▶️  "And all the Noxian High Command couldn't put Riven together again." is a play on a quote from Humpty Dumpty.
    • ▶️  "Scissors... beats... paper." references Rock–paper–scissors.
    • ▶️  "Never go full machine." is a play on a quote from Tropic Thunder ("You never go full retard.").
    • ▶️  "Not all dogs go to heaven." references All Dogs Go to Heaven.
    • ▶️  " Monkey see, monkey die!" references an American pidgin.
  • Camille's joke ▶️  "A Noxian, a Zaunite and a Freljordian walk into my blade. The end." resembles Diana's ▶️  "A man, a woman and a yordle walk into the sun. They die! Because it burns them alive?"
Program Camille
  • ▶️  "You must be coded as a minion." references the game developers' tendency to code many objects as minions.
  • ▶️  "You chose... poorly." references Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade.
  • ▶️   "I'll be back." and ▶️  "Terminated." quote The Terminator.
    • She shares this quote with ▶️   Sion.
  • ▶️  "That was the sound of inevitability." quotes The Matrix.
    • She shares this quote with:
      • ▶️   PROJECT: Vayne
      • ▶️   Pulsefire Caitlyn
  • Camille shares quotes with:
    • ▶️   ▶️   "End of the line."
